[
  {
    "speaker": "char_lu_shi_xiong",
    "speaker_name": "鲁世雄",
    "listener": "char_du_gu_fei_feng",
    "text": "我出身卑微，自知不配高攀格格，格格对这头婚事，若然不乐意的话——",
    "tone": "犹豫",
    "chapter": 4,
    "line_start": 16,
    "line_end": 18
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_du_gu_fei_feng",
    "speaker_name": "独孤飞凤",
    "listener": "char_lu_shi_xiong",
    "text": "你别这样说，我和你一样，都是孤儿。你的爹爹是檀元帅的下属，我的爹爹也不过是王爷的家将，只要你不嫌我，我已经是满意了。",
    "tone": "温柔",
    "chapter": 4,
    "line_start": 20,
    "line_end": 22
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_lu_shi_xiong",
    "speaker_name": "鲁世雄",
    "listener": "char_du_gu_fei_feng",
    "text": "那么，娘子是另有心事？",
    "tone": "疑问",
    "chapter": 4,
    "line_start": 24,
    "line_end": 26
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_du_gu_fei_feng",
    "speaker_name": "独孤飞凤",
    "listener": "char_lu_shi_xiong",
    "text": "不错，我是另有心事。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 4,
    "line_start": 28,
    "line_end": 28
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_lu_shi_xiong",
    "speaker_name": "鲁世雄",
    "listener": "char_du_gu_fei_feng",
    "text": "不知格格可以说给我听么？",
    "tone": "疑问",
    "chapter": 4,
    "line_start": 30,
    "line_end": 32
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_du_gu_fei_feng",
    "speaker_name": "独孤飞凤",
    "listener": "char_lu_shi_xiong",
    "text": "你娶我为妻，是迫于王爷命令还是真心真意地喜欢我？",
    "tone": "认真",
    "chapter": 4,
    "line_start": 36,
    "line_end": 38
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_lu_shi_xiong",
    "speaker_name": "鲁世雄",
    "listener": "char_du_gu_fei_feng",
    "text": "格格才貌双绝，不啻无人，小可得遇格格，只有自惭形秽，夫复何求？",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 4,
    "line_start": 40,
    "line_end": 42
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_du_gu_fei_feng",
    "speaker_name": "独孤飞凤",
    "listener": "char_lu_shi_xiong",
    "text": "那么，你真的喜欢我了？",
    "tone": "认真",
    "chapter": 4,
    "line_start": 46,
    "line_end": 46
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_lu_shi_xiong",
    "speaker_name": "鲁世雄",
    "listener": "char_du_gu_fei_feng",
    "text": "但愿一生长伺妆台，听格格的差遣。",
    "tone": "认真",
    "chapter": 4,
    "line_start": 48,
    "line_end": 48
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_du_gu_fei_feng",
    "speaker_name": "独孤飞凤",
    "listener": "char_lu_shi_xiong",
    "text": "你真的肯对我百依百顺，我说什么你都听我的话？",
    "tone": "欣喜",
    "chapter": 4,
    "line_start": 50,
    "line_end": 52
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_lu_shi_xiong",
    "speaker_name": "鲁世雄",
    "listener": "char_du_gu_fei_feng",
    "text": "赴汤蹈火，在所不辞。",
    "tone": "认真",
    "chapter": 4,
    "line_start": 54,
    "line_end": 54
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_du_gu_fei_feng",
    "speaker_name": "独孤飞凤",
    "listener": "char_lu_shi_xiong",
    "text": "好，那么今晚就要你做一件事情，你可能做到？",
    "tone": "认真",
    "chapter": 4,
    "line_start": 56,
    "line_end": 56
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_lu_shi_xiong",
    "speaker_name": "鲁世雄",
    "listener": "char_du_gu_fei_feng",
    "text": "请格格吩咐。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 4,
    "line_start": 58,
    "line_end": 58
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_du_gu_fei_feng",
    "speaker_name": "独孤飞凤",
    "listener": "char_lu_shi_xiong",
    "text": "我要你今晚去杀一个人！",
    "tone": "严肃",
    "chapter": 4,
    "line_start": 60,
    "line_end": 62
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_lu_shi_xiong",
    "speaker_name": "鲁世雄",
    "listener": "char_du_gu_fei_feng",
    "text": "娘子是说笑吧？洞房之夜去杀人，岂不辜负了良宵花烛？",
    "tone": "轻笑",
    "chapter": 4,
    "line_start": 66,
    "line_end": 68
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_du_gu_fei_feng",
    "speaker_name": "独孤飞凤",
    "listener": "char_lu_shi_xiong",
    "text": "谁和你说笑了，五更之前，你不把那人的首级拿回来，你就休想再进洞房！",
    "tone": "严肃",
    "chapter": 4,
    "line_start": 70,
    "line_end": 70
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_lu_shi_xiong",
    "speaker_name": "鲁世雄",
    "listener": "char_du_gu_fei_feng",
    "text": "好，我去就是。你要杀谁？",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 4,
    "line_start": 72,
    "line_end": 72
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_du_gu_fei_feng",
    "speaker_name": "独孤飞凤",
    "listener": "char_lu_shi_xiong",
    "text": "长安街有条皮帽胡同，皮帽胡同里有一间名叫昌业的皮货店，皮货店里有一个老板，姓杨。有一天我去买狐裘，他对我出言无礼，甚不恭敬，你去给我一剑杀了！",
    "tone": "愤怒",
    "chapter": 4,
    "line_start": 74,
    "line_end": 74
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_lu_shi_xiong",
    "speaker_name": "鲁世雄",
    "listener": "char_du_gu_fei_feng",
    "text": "为了这点小事就杀一个人，这——",
    "tone": "苦笑",
    "chapter": 4,
    "line_start": 76,
    "line_end": 78
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_du_gu_fei_feng",
    "speaker_name": "独孤飞凤",
    "listener": "char_lu_shi_xiong",
    "text": "你说这是太过份了，是不是？",
    "tone": "愤怒",
    "chapter": 4,
    "line_start": 82,
    "line_end": 82
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_lu_shi_xiong",
    "speaker_name": "鲁世雄",
    "listener": "char_du_gu_fei_feng",
    "text": "不敢。不过，人命关天，那人似乎罪不至死。",
    "tone": "犹豫",
    "chapter": 4,
    "line_start": 84,
    "line_end": 84
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_du_gu_fei_feng",
    "speaker_name": "独孤飞凤",
    "listener": "char_lu_shi_xiong",
    "text": "他调戏了我，还是件小事？你刚才怎么答着？哼，哼，说得倒好——任从格格差遣，赴汤蹈火，在所不辞——怎么你现在又推三阻四了？你是不是识得那姓杨的，下不了手。",
    "tone": "愤怒",
    "chapter": 4,
    "line_start": 86,
    "line_end": 90
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_lu_shi_xiong",
    "speaker_name": "鲁世雄",
    "listener": "char_du_gu_fei_feng",
    "text": "好，我马上就去。五更之前，把他的首级送回来给你。",
    "tone": "认真",
    "chapter": 4,
    "line_start": 92,
    "line_end": 94
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_du_gu_fei_feng",
    "speaker_name": "独孤飞凤",
    "listener": "char_lu_shi_xiong",
    "text": "你听清楚了。这个杨老板年约三十，中等身材，短发浓须，左颊有个金钱般大小的疤痕，最易记认。你可不要杀错了人！",
    "tone": "认真",
    "chapter": 4,
    "line_start": 96,
    "line_end": 96
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_lu_shi_xiong",
    "speaker_name": "鲁世雄",
    "listener": "char_du_gu_fei_feng",
    "text": "是，你说得这样清楚，我决不会杀错的。我这就去啦！",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 4,
    "line_start": 98,
    "line_end": 98
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_lu_shi_xiong",
    "speaker_name": "鲁世雄",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "想不到王爷还是信不过我。呀，这才是一次真正要命的考试！",
    "tone": "苦笑",
    "chapter": 4,
    "line_start": 116,
    "line_end": 116
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_lu_shi_xiong",
    "speaker_name": "鲁世雄",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "去呢还是不去？杀呢还是不杀？",
    "tone": "犹豫",
    "chapter": 4,
    "line_start": 142,
    "line_end": 142
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_du_gu_fei_feng",
    "speaker_name": "独孤飞凤",
    "listener": "char_wan_yan_chang_zhi",
    "text": "你猜他去呢还是不去？杀呢还是不杀？",
    "tone": "疑问",
    "chapter": 4,
    "line_start": 148,
    "line_end": 148
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_wan_yan_chang_zhi",
    "speaker_name": "完颜长之",
    "listener": "char_du_gu_fei_feng",
    "text": "此事我也难以猜测。好在只有两个时辰就可以揭晓了。他若是杀了此人，那么咱们就可以完全信任他了。否则他就一定是南朝的奸细！",
    "tone": "轻笑",
    "chapter": 4,
    "line_start": 152,
    "line_end": 154
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_du_gu_fei_feng",
    "speaker_name": "独孤飞凤",
    "listener": "char_wan_yan_chang_zhi",
    "text": "倘若他是真心真意地效忠父王，但还不是丧在那姓杨的金刀之下？——",
    "tone": "担心",
    "chapter": 4,
    "line_start": 156,
    "line_end": 158
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_wan_yan_chang_zhi",
    "speaker_name": "完颜长之",
    "listener": "char_du_gu_fei_feng",
    "text": "这个你倒不用担心，我已派了两名心腹高手跟在他的后面。只要他是真正的力战不敌，在最后关头，那两个高手自会助他。倘若他想一走了之，溜出大都的话，那么，那两个高手就会把他杀了。凤儿，你是不是爱惜他呢。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 4,
    "line_start": 160,
    "line_end": 160
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_du_gu_fei_feng",
    "speaker_name": "独孤飞凤",
    "listener": "char_wan_yan_chang_zhi",
    "text": "他若然背叛父王，我又岂能要他做我的丈夫？爹，你不杀他，我也会杀他的！",
    "tone": "认真",
    "chapter": 4,
    "line_start": 164,
    "line_end": 164
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_wan_yan_chang_zhi",
    "speaker_name": "完颜长之",
    "listener": "char_du_gu_fei_feng",
    "text": "我之所以要如此试他，都是为了你的原故。你想，倘若不能证明他确实可靠，我岂能让他不伎在研经院中，任他每日来回？他若是不能每日来回，你嫁了他，也就没有什么夫妇之乐了。你要懂得我的苦心才好。",
    "tone": "认真",
    "chapter": 4,
    "line_start": 172,
    "line_end": 174
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_du_gu_fei_feng",
    "speaker_name": "独孤飞凤",
    "listener": "char_wan_yan_chang_zhi",
    "text": "孩儿懂得，多谢父王。",
    "tone": "温柔",
    "chapter": 4,
    "line_start": 176,
    "line_end": 178
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_wan_yan_chang_zhi",
    "speaker_name": "char_wan_yan_chang_zhi",
    "listener": "char_du_gu_fei_feng",
    "text": "我为了这样试他，还当真觉得可惜呢！",
    "tone": "轻笑",
    "chapter": 4,
    "line_start": 182,
    "line_end": 184
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_du_gu_fei_feng",
    "speaker_name": "独孤飞凤",
    "listener": "char_wan_yan_chang_zhi",
    "text": "父王可惜什么？",
    "tone": "好奇",
    "chapter": 4,
    "line_start": 186,
    "line_end": 186
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_wan_yan_chang_zhi",
    "speaker_name": "完颜长之",
    "listener": "char_du_gu_fei_feng",
    "text": "你知道我是早已识破了那姓杨的身份的了，我要杀他，易如反掌，却为什么要留到现在，才叫鲁世雄去杀他。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 4,
    "line_start": 188,
    "line_end": 190
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_du_gu_fei_feng",
    "speaker_name": "独孤飞凤",
    "listener": "char_wan_yan_chang_zhi",
    "text": "父王可是为了要放长线，钓大鱼！",
    "tone": "惊讶",
    "chapter": 4,
    "line_start": 192,
    "line_end": 194
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_wan_yan_chang_zhi",
    "speaker_name": "完颜长之",
    "listener": "char_du_gu_fei_feng",
    "text": "凤儿，你真聪明，一猜就着！留下这姓杨的和那间皮货店，江南来的人，就逃不过咱们的耳目，这不比只杀了一个姓杨的好得多吗？如今为你的原故，我必须这样来试世雄，以后侦察南朝的奸细，我还得另费一番心机呢。",
    "tone": "得意",
    "chapter": 4,
    "line_start": 196,
    "line_end": 198
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_du_gu_fei_feng",
    "speaker_name": "独孤飞凤",
    "listener": "char_wan_yan_chang_zhi",
    "text": "爹爹这样为了孩儿！孩儿感激不尽。",
    "tone": "欣喜",
    "chapter": 4,
    "line_start": 200,
    "line_end": 200
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_wan_yan_chang_zhi",
    "speaker_name": "完颜长之",
    "listener": "char_du_gu_fei_feng",
    "text": "你在担心他过不了这场考试？",
    "tone": "轻笑",
    "chapter": 4,
    "line_start": 204,
    "line_end": 206
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_wan_yan_chang_zhi",
    "speaker_name": "完颜长之",
    "listener": "char_du_gu_fei_feng",
    "text": "就快五更了，你再等片刻，这个闷葫芦就可以打破了。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 4,
    "line_start": 208,
    "line_end": 210
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_wan_yan_chang_zhi",
    "speaker_name": "完颜长之",
    "listener": "char_du_gu_fei_feng",
    "text": "好了，你可以放心了。他回来了！",
    "tone": "欣喜",
    "chapter": 4,
    "line_start": 214,
    "line_end": 216
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_wan_yan_chang_zhi",
    "speaker_name": "完颜长之",
    "listener": "char_du_gu_fei_feng",
    "text": "咱们去迎接他吧！",
    "tone": "轻笑",
    "chapter": 4,
    "line_start": 222,
    "line_end": 224
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_du_gu_fei_feng",
    "speaker_name": "独孤飞凤",
    "listener": "char_lu_shi_xiong",
    "text": "世雄，你受伤了。",
    "tone": "担心",
    "chapter": 4,
    "line_start": 232,
    "line_end": 234
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_lu_shi_xiong",
    "speaker_name": "鲁世雄",
    "listener": "char_wan_yan_chang_zhi",
    "text": "岳父大人，你还没睡。",
    "tone": "惊讶",
    "chapter": 4,
    "line_start": 236,
    "line_end": 238
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_lu_shi_xiong",
    "speaker_name": "鲁世雄",
    "listener": "char_du_gu_fei_feng",
    "text": "不要紧，我虽然给斫了两刀，幸好不是伤着要害。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 4,
    "line_start": 240,
    "line_end": 242
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_lu_shi_xiong",
    "speaker_name": "鲁世雄",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "看来她对我确是有了几分真情了。",
    "tone": "欣慰",
    "chapter": 4,
    "line_start": 248,
    "line_end": 248
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_wan_yan_chang_zhi",
    "speaker_name": "完颜长之",
    "listener": "char_lu_shi_xiong",
    "text": "我听说凤儿叫你去杀人，我放心不下，在这里等你，嗯，你的伤虽不很重但也不轻呢，先到我的书房裹伤再说吧。",
    "tone": "担心",
    "chapter": 4,
    "line_start": 250,
    "line_end": 252
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_lu_shi_xiong",
    "speaker_name": "鲁世雄",
    "listener": "char_du_gu_fei_feng",
    "text": "幸不辱命，请你看看这个首级，是否杀错了人。",
    "tone": "轻笑",
    "chapter": 4,
    "line_start": 256,
    "line_end": 258
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_du_gu_fei_feng",
    "speaker_name": "独孤飞凤",
    "listener": "char_lu_shi_xiong",
    "text": "一点不错。你把这姓杨的杀了！",
    "tone": "欣喜",
    "chapter": 4,
    "line_start": 262,
    "line_end": 262
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_lu_shi_xiong",
    "speaker_name": "鲁世雄",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "留下这姓杨的好处固然是有，但也不无害处。杀了他我总是少了一个对手。",
    "tone": "平静",
    "chapter": 4,
    "line_start": 266,
    "line_end": 266
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_du_gu_fei_feng",
    "speaker_name": "独孤飞凤",
    "listener": "char_lu_shi_xiong",
    "text": "这姓杨的刀法很厉害吧？",
    "tone": "好奇",
    "chapter": 4,
    "line_start": 268,
    "line_end": 268
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_lu_shi_xiong",
    "speaker_name": "鲁世雄",
    "listener": "char_du_gu_fei_feng",
    "text": "厉害极了。我以为我会丧命在他刀下的呢，谁知到了最紧要的关头，他砍出一刀，不知怎的竟是软绵绵毫无力道，我抓紧机会，这才一剑将他杀死，心中可是犹有余悸。",
    "tone": "痛苦",
    "chapter": 4,
    "line_start": 270,
    "line_end": 271
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_wan_yan_chang_zhi",
    "speaker_name": "完颜长之",
    "listener": "char_lu_shi_xiong",
    "text": "你要知道这原因吗？我告诉你。",
    "tone": "微笑",
    "chapter": 4,
    "line_start": 272,
    "line_end": 274
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_lu_shi_xiong",
    "speaker_name": "鲁世雄",
    "listener": "char_wan_yan_chang_zhi",
    "text": "多谢岳父派人相助，那'杨老板'原来是这两位大哥杀的！",
    "tone": "惊讶",
    "chapter": 4,
    "line_start": 278,
    "line_end": 280
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_hei_yi_ren",
    "speaker_name": "黑衣人",
    "listener": "char_lu_shi_xiong",
    "text": "不，是郡马杀的，倘若不是郡马奋力勇战，教那姓杨的不得不全神应付，我们的暗器焉能得手？",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 4,
    "line_start": 284,
    "line_end": 284
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_wan_yan_chang_zhi",
    "speaker_name": "完颜长之",
    "listener": "char_hei_yi_ren",
    "text": "你们可以下去了，给我按照原定的计划，尽捕那姓杨的党羽！",
    "tone": "严肃",
    "chapter": 4,
    "line_start": 286,
    "line_end": 288
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_du_gu_fei_feng",
    "speaker_name": "独孤飞凤",
    "listener": "char_wan_yan_chang_zhi",
    "text": "要这么着急？",
    "tone": "轻笑",
    "chapter": 4,
    "line_start": 292,
    "line_end": 292
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_wan_yan_chang_zhi",
    "speaker_name": "完颜长之",
    "listener": "char_du_gu_fei_feng",
    "text": "那姓杨的皮货店本来要在今天搬的，他一搬走，他的手下的住址也就要改动了，所以必须在今天一网打尽。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 4,
    "line_start": 294,
    "line_end": 296
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_wan_yan_chang_zhi",
    "speaker_name": "完颜长之",
    "listener": "char_lu_shi_xiong",
    "text": "恭喜贤婿，立了大功！",
    "tone": "得意",
    "chapter": 4,
    "line_start": 304,
    "line_end": 306
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_lu_shi_xiong",
    "speaker_name": "鲁世雄",
    "listener": "char_wan_yan_chang_zhi",
    "text": "杀一个皮货店的老板，何功之有？",
    "tone": "疑问",
    "chapter": 4,
    "line_start": 308,
    "line_end": 310
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_wan_yan_chang_zhi",
    "speaker_name": "完颜长之",
    "listener": "char_lu_shi_xiong",
    "text": "他有这样好的武功，岂会只是一个皮货店的老板，我告诉你他的真正身份吧。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 4,
    "line_start": 312,
    "line_end": 312
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_lu_shi_xiong",
    "speaker_name": "鲁世雄",
    "listener": "char_wan_yan_chang_zhi",
    "text": "我也猜想得到他不是一个寻常的人物，但却想不到他竟是江南来的奸细头子！",
    "tone": "惊讶",
    "chapter": 4,
    "line_start": 314,
    "line_end": 316
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_lu_shi_xiong",
    "speaker_name": "鲁世雄",
    "listener": "char_wan_yan_chang_zhi",
    "text": "小婿也要恭喜岳父大人消除了一个祸患。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 4,
    "line_start": 322,
    "line_end": 322
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_wan_yan_chang_zhi",
    "speaker_name": "完颜长之",
    "listener": "char_lu_shi_xiong",
    "text": "还有一个更大的祸患呢！这人神出鬼没，虽然不一定是受命于南宋，却比那姓杨的更难对付！",
    "tone": "严肃",
    "chapter": 4,
    "line_start": 324,
    "line_end": 326
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_lu_shi_xiong",
    "speaker_name": "鲁世雄",
    "listener": "char_wan_yan_chang_zhi",
    "text": "那人是谁？",
    "tone": "惊讶",
    "chapter": 4,
    "line_start": 328,
    "line_end": 328
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_wan_yan_chang_zhi",
    "speaker_name": "完颜长之",
    "listener": "char_lu_shi_xiong",
    "text": "无人知道他真名实姓，只知他的外号，人称南海潜龙！这条'潜龙'潜入了大都，我们的人四出搜查，人未捕到，反而给他杀了咱们的十几名好手。今后也许还要贤婿出力呢。",
    "tone": "严肃",
    "chapter": 4,
    "line_start": 330,
    "line_end": 332
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_lu_shi_xiong",
    "speaker_name": "鲁世雄",
    "listener": "char_wan_yan_chang_zhi",
    "text": "若有用到小婿之处，小婚自当效力。",
    "tone": "认真",
    "chapter": 4,
    "line_start": 334,
    "line_end": 336
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_wan_yan_chang_zhi",
    "speaker_name": "完颜长之",
    "listener": "char_lu_shi_xiong",
    "text": "好，你回房歇息吧。你立了大功，但却误了你们的花烛良宵了。",
    "tone": "轻笑",
    "chapter": 4,
    "line_start": 338,
    "line_end": 340
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_lu_shi_xiong",
    "speaker_name": "鲁世雄",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "谁是潜龙？谁是潜龙？",
    "tone": "疑问",
    "chapter": 4,
    "line_start": 344,
    "line_end": 344
  }
]